This is my very first server and I hope you enjoy it. editted a little by me Dead Eyez and My coder Fridder Credits to:
60% to Rune Slay for the source. 10% Edited a little by me Dead Eyez. 30% Coded by Fridder.
Download the Client here: * Also to connect to my server you need hamachi, And if you don't got it just search it on Google by typing in Hamachi Download. (I will be adding pictures soon.) Then you will be all set because my client has got my hamachi ip in it. You just need hamachi cause i don't know my routers username and password :(. so sorry for you guys that hate Hamachi but let me tell you something this is my first server with:
100% working soul wars!!! Summoning familiars!! Owner is: Dead Eyez. Co-Owner is: Fridder. (The coder) 100% agility! 100% real skillcape emotes! 100% real barrows! Dark Bow's hit like real runescape double hit 100%! Granite Maul spec Works 100%!! Firemaking 100%! Woodcutting 100%! Theiving 100%! Fishing 100%! Hunting 100%! Agility 100%! Mining 100%! Cooking 100%! Crafting gives amulets instead of cut stones 100%! (craft a onyx get an amulet of fury!) Basic Fletching 100%! Herblore 100%! Runecrafting 100%! Smithing 100%! Many Specs!! Working lamps 100%! Warriors Guild 100%! Working Anchor 100%! Awesome home! =p new yell colors! fast prayer training, 30k xp a bone!!! :eek: extreme potions!! :cool: Multi Barrage! Miasmic Spells! Clan Wars Free for all! Pest Control 100%! Awesome Bosses!! Mandrith buys your pvp drops! (statuettes,etc) REAL PvP Drops! Venge other 100%! Balance Elemental, which uses 3 different attack styles! Cape Trimming! Like i said i will be posting pictures soon goodluck and hope to be seeing you in game! :).
